            <h4 class="text-lg font-semibold mb-2 text-accent">Communication Style</h4>
            <p class="mb-3 text-gray-300"><strong>Direct and explicit</strong> communication with clear, straightforward language. Americans value "getting to the point" and typically use detailed, comprehensive written agreements.</p>
            {/* Example Box Styling */}
